As for the assistant to Mamaev Vasily Seroshtanov, the court did not establish the circumstances that would become the basis for changing the category of the severity of the offense and changing the sentence.
Anton Mamaev himself said that he was dissatisfied with the decision of the Moscow City Court.
I am disappointed with the court&#39;s decision.
The only legal solution would be to justify, intends to continue to fight for justice.
